Return

$DEF_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGFTDUOF
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "FTDUOF" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [TOF2]
& As [TOF2]
Titled [TOF2] TIT
Return

$VISU_BOITE
Gosub INIT_BOITE
Gosub HORODAT From WGFTDUOF
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Inpbox "FTDUOF" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [TOF2]
& As [TOF2]
Titled [TOF2] TIT
Gosub AFF_BOITE
Return

$AFF_BOITE
Boxact [TOF2] 
Return

$SAISIE_BOITE
